            <field name="employee_feedback" type="html">
                <h2>
                    <strong>
                        My work
                    </strong>
                </h2>
                <h3>What are my most important achievements since my last appraisal?</h3>
                <p>
                    <em>
                        Describe something you are proud of—work that had a positive impact on
                        the company.
                    </em>
                </p>
                <p>
                    When I realized the project was falling behind schedule, I quickly organized a
                    team meeting to identify the bottlenecks. By reallocating resources and setting
                    clear priorities, we managed to get back on track and deliver on time.
                </p>
                <h3>
                  What has been the most challenging aspect of my work this past year,
                  and why?
                </h3>
                <p>
                    <em>
                        Did you face any new difficulties or unexpected obstacles?
                    </em>
                </p>
                <p>
                    Working with diverse team personalities can lead to significant challenges, such
                    as misunderstandings due to differing communication styles and frustration from
                    varying levels of motivation. These differences often create tension and
                    conflict, making collaboration difficult and hindering overall productivity.
                    When team members clash, it can result in resentment and a lack of cohesion,
                    ultimately impacting the success of our projects.
                </p>
                <h3>What do I need to improve my work?</h3>
                <p>
                    <em>
                        How can the company support your needs and objectives to help you 
                        reach your goals and foster better collaboration?
                    </em>
                </p>
                <p>
                    During my appraisal, I wanted to bring up something that I believe could really
                    help me perform better in my role. I’ve been reflecting on the challenges we
                    sometimes face in managing issues and communicating effectively, especially in
                    high-pressure situations.
                </p>
                <p>
                    I think it would be incredibly beneficial for me to receive some training on
                    issues management and positive communication. I believe that with the right
                    tools and techniques, I could handle challenges more proactively and foster a
                    more positive environment within the team. This training would not only enhance
                    my skills but also contribute to our overall team dynamics and productivity.
                </p>
                <p>
                    I’m committed to doing my best work, and I truly believe that this kind of
                    training would be a valuable investment in my development. What do you think?
                </p>
                <h2>
                    <strong>
                        My future
                    </strong>
                </h2>
                <h3>
                    What are my short- and long-term goals within the company and for my
                    career?
